data.description: Owner looking for offer!!  Beautiful, landscaped property featuring a well-maintained Ranch with full basement.  3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, both have been remodeled, Large eat in kitchen with lots of cabinets, range & refrigerator stay.  The washer & dryer are currently set up in the bedroom but can be moved back to the full basement, they will convey with the property.  2 fireplaces, not warranted, get your own inspection.   Enjoy the beautiful back yard from covered patio. Well maintained home, See it today!
